NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION AND PERMANENCY, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
K.E., Defendant-Petitioner,
and
C.L.L., Defendant. In the Matter of the Guardianship of C.G.L., a Minor-Respondent. C-639 September Term 2018
082081 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 8, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-004064-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
